Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来安乐冈同学最近有什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:25.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你最近都不和粟屋一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说是又想找我商量我才过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会讲到我的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为安乐冈同学的话很有参考价值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是俊男美女的情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,备受大家瞩目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以当然会在意你们怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从暑假之后就没见过面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,十月都结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:04.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…感觉现在不见面会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:27.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来皆川老师你意外地容易亲近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正伪装也没用了 不装了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校也这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还要继续呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这已经成了毕生的事业？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那种事根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天风有点大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽快干脆地搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是种怎样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:52.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要先休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:01.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去倒水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说为什么那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我真的喝不了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一口闷 一口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,酒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:59.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和母亲来过一次温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:03.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,星星应该很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜了 不戴眼镜基本看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像做梦一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和皆川老师一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:19.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在房间里一起看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我总在关键时刻掉链子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想和她一起看星星的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你眼镜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请你别笑 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是鲜花抑或繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这世间一切美好的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了比喻你而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得房间太暗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暗才好 我想看月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么暗的话更加看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说「不用停下来」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不记得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢玩男人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是喜欢才做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不用停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么被你说的像兴趣一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然是因为喜欢才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,需要想？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,需要想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在紧张些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:27.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望你不讨厌这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不讨厌你 你就会讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:42.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸 这什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,节奏全都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:50.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你喜欢的人讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能否一直喜欢她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分人都会说不吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说 「喜欢对方」这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:22.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,往往包含了「对方也喜欢自己」的前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无条件的喜欢别人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:28.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:30.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:45.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要说明喜欢的理由太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你还是个语文老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:11.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的人能健康地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来像是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:32.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个答案我还不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦产生了需求 便会永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欲望无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:02.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子终有一日 会伤害重要的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 并不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很渴望 很渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是特别的伤的话也足够让人变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:46.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么 舒服的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能 拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,身在其中的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了这么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会说自己断片了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆…茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是 名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和…和我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,江山易改 本性难移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在也是充满着算计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感情说不定也只是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:12.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你很多绿帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绿帽子也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要去弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是否真的是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人会改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:50.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害 像初次约会一样的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是由咱 由我 由在下改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看见经别人改变的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 但是之前去过咖啡店了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊咧 约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的约会也一定会成为 最后的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢高处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 让人欢欣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样从天空俯视大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前的人们都是做不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾发生过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:39.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了茜姐内心真正的声音的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像喜欢教别人些什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得的话也不会做这份兼职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:00.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 想在死的时候也不留在任何人的记忆里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是反了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和正在做着的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教师不是影响他人的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:15.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,成为老师的话 在大家的记忆中也不过一直是老师而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间 感觉明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:24.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人 不把自己套用在些什么身份上就会不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 女人 年上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望把这些身份背在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后局限于那个无聊的地方里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:37.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实比谁都希望着自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:42.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我终会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,将你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的很高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有同样的理由喜欢它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:02.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难得现在有新的东西能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就想试试看那样啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的事增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样让人感觉到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:11.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要将你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:24.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新的事情 做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想去尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被我而是被谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:47.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被仅有的一个命中注定 无可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐已经不是老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是一个只想让男人承认价值就满足了的寂寞女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于拥有了名字与实体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那迈出新步伐的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美得不可方物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊那啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多想要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:14.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那谢谢你了 送到这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的是很喜欢小麦的脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我是过分的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得 但不会责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有怪责的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我结果只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个不软弱不狡猾不是「女人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法生存下去的那时候的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,充满着爱慕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 会一直记得的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论茜姐多想忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想要改变你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,改变前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:38.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:40.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:19.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
